# Copy to .env.local for local overrides. For production, set the same keys in the
# Vercel dashboard: Project → Settings → Environment Variables.

# This app has no required environment variables. Wikipedia is called directly from
# the browser (https://en.wikipedia.org/w/api.php) with no API keys.

# If you add client-side configuration later, use the Vite convention and prefix
# with VITE_ so values are exposed to import.meta.env (e.g. VITE_API_URL).
# VITE_API_URL=
